Roger Sterling is a child.

3
00:00:04,123 --> 00:00:06,429
Still I expect pragmatism from you...

4
00:00:06,943 --> 00:00:07,945
We share that...

5
00:00:08,093 --> 00:00:11,430
I just keep thinking about
what's going on here and I miss it.

6
00:00:11,533 --> 00:00:12,677
I say we put it to a vote.

7
00:00:12,775 --> 00:00:14,116
I say we step outside.

8
00:00:14,429 --> 00:00:18,271
Allison and Faye Miller and
who knows how many more...

9
00:00:18,410 --> 00:00:20,171
I'm going to be with
you until I die.

10
00:00:20,508 --> 00:00:22,091
How's not your wife
dropping you off?

11
00:00:22,330 --> 00:00:24,856
There was a time when she
wouldn't leave the house in a robe.

12
00:00:24,957 --> 00:00:29,042
There's a point when you go from
going home on the 5:25 to the 7:05.

13
